summary:
Moomin: If Little My and I were both drowning, who would you save?
Snufkin: I don’t know, both of you.
Moomin: No, if you could...
body:
Moomin: If Little My and I were both drowning, who would you save?
Snufkin: I don’t know, both of you.
Moomin: No, if you could only save one of us.
Snufkin: Well, I would probably save Little My, because she can’t swim and I happen to know you’re an excellent swimmer.
Moomin: What if I was holding an anchor? Who would you save then?
Snufkin: Well, why don’t you just let go of the anchor?
Moomin: It’s a family heirloom.
Snufkin: I’m leaving.

summary: Joxter not only likes messing with people by scaring them but also likes to mindfuck with them too by giving them hallucinations...
question: Joxter not only likes messing with people by scaring them but also likes to mindfuck with them too by giving them hallucinations and nightmares. Sometimes moominpappa, or anyone else besides Snufkin, will dream that Joxter is in their room just staring at them while smiling but then they’ll wake up and wonder if it was just a nightmare or if he really was in their room.
answer: YEAH not only nightmares but also… sleep paralysis. joxter gets an absolute kick out of this shit. this is the main contributing factor to moominpappa’s ever growing paranoia and sleep deprivation. he just decides “well, maybe if I Don’t Sleep, This Won’t Happen” … too bad he can’t avoid passing out forever
